column5: i will be leaving this weekend for a week at tall pines...any fishing info would be great.... any one going to be there also 6/10/06 - 06/17/06 thanks for your time wayne[email protected]
We just got back this week. Fish were biting every where.We didn't use any live bait, all jig with tail works for us. Have fun!

Was up over Memorial Day weekend. Caught 5 northerns over 38" and multiple eyes over 22" with largest at 28". Average size of the eyes was around 18". Fishing was very good as we caught fish in most areas we targeted. We stayed at Peffley's Camp. Very nice and away from the rest of the camps. Heartguy
